{"tid":1740000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[思想武裝] 香港已經冇法律，呢個就係我地面對緊既世界","createTime":"2019-11-19T21:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T04:50:00.000Z","uid":154486,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f50ce783249968c8d92afe0648be4d5d90d608ff","tid":1740000,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:13:36.000Z","msg":"人大講得好清楚<br />\n<strong>人大講既野就係法律，共產黨就係法律<br />\n而家所有所謂程序都係過去既遺留物</strong><br />\n<br />\n好快律師唔可以再見犯，冇得保釋，你冇野講都寫到你有野講，無限期拘留你打到你變屎餅<br />\n比人拉告暴動，就算告唔入都會告得入<br />\n<br />\n曱甴永遠唔會犯法，當街先姦後殺都唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n美國英國歐洲出口術，未見棺材唔識喊，一味叫人唔好勇武，但係原來勇武畫面對佢地先係最有效<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個就係我地面對既世界</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點算？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>和理非升級做勇武</strong>，打游擊戰開花學下點整同出火魔聖水水魔屎魔蟲魔，擺陣行軍撤退<br />\n<br />\n<strong>勇武全面地下化</strong>，我唔要見到有live片或者圖，我淨係想見到個結果<br />\n<br />\n<strong>咁多位和理非<br />\n法律呢一樣工具，已經唔適用係香港</strong><br />\n唔需要再強調對家犯左乜野法<br />\n<br />\n<strong>對家係永遠唔會犯法</strong><br />\n但係佢一捉到你，你就犯左法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">法律已經<strong>唔存在</strong></span><br />\n請將「犯法」兩個字係字典上面刪除<br />\n<br />\n以後只有<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>「全身而退」</strong><br />\n以及<br />\n<strong>「失敗被擒」</strong></span></span><br />\n兩個可能性<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地係納粹治下既波蘭，東德治下既東柏林<br />\n<strong>法律只係借口，武力先係正道</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<ins>我地係反抗軍，係革命軍，係邪惡入面永不磨滅既正義</ins><br />\n你有冇聽過比人拉左既反抗軍可以靠打官司脫罪？<br />\n<br />\n黎明來臨之前係最撚黑暗<br />\n所以<br />\n要黎明到來，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">先要承認自己身陷黑暗<br />\n唔好再呃自己仲有一線星光<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n跟我講一次：<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">香港不存在法律</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔好再比法律束縛自己！"},{"pid":"be43db2a884def6df26e92515ea90fef6f4f7256","tid":1740000,"uid":154486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:16:50.000Z","msg":"推上去破除心魔"},{"pid":"d76dab40750ad011400e38cdfa11860133084da9","tid":1740000,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:38:31.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"b19022c6dc5221d09d365e15cad0a5b36f4fbe2f","tid":1740000,"uid":340987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:42:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afa5c49279514fd8f90e772a75f21a1267a3e029","tid":1740000,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:45:05.000Z","msg":"推呀屌你"},{"pid":"d28fe448b4fedf21ed37de14f6a01147bc1e933b","tid":1740000,"uid":299582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:47:07.000Z","msg":"正確"},{"pid":"32bc3f0f9d376063c30298b79f737d3472bc0d70","tid":1740000,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T21:59:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4aa3e687eb7a0ff420c09da9f7468e2d8dde77f5","tid":1740000,"uid":174294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:00:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaa561d0d748ab6e994df708ba02648f702a0dbe","tid":1740000,"uid":218242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:19:58.000Z","msg":"方向正確"},{"pid":"839d3c76a51d597c2353480a8b74132e0eeafa74","tid":1740000,"uid":114328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8991290226a5907552359f41e8b503ed5710780a","tid":1740000,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:21:20.000Z","msg":"我要返工！"},{"pid":"8c59ea14f136422c5db1a67ab47e899d8e3098f8","tid":1740000,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:21:36.000Z","msg":"唔想勇武全面地下化，佢地越地下化，只會越黎越孤獨，要齊上齊落，唔使孤身奮戰。"},{"pid":"e5a2aa754c100503f69719e43150137e2db174f9","tid":1740000,"uid":191924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:22:03.000Z","msg":"push la大撚把豬未醒"},{"pid":"55b5fef91e67f835d9d297c4d529b3a2c51c19cb","tid":1740000,"uid":154486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c59ea14f136422c5db1a67ab47e899d8e3098f8","tid":1740000,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:21:36.000Z","msg":"唔想勇武全面地下化，佢地越地下化，只會越黎越孤獨，要齊上齊落，唔使孤身奮戰。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T22:29:37.000Z","msg":"所以先要由和理非升級做地面勇武"},{"pid":"88b57ea0f6fdbf0f5a3188bad56e17ba69c25b44","tid":1740000,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:22:59.000Z","msg":"推上去"},{"pid":"1d15485d929bc57a56a157d42c25b5275d7e6bd6","tid":1740000,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:29:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a528c6d5db144559a2f275d3bfbf3a7d6e49cb4a","tid":1740000,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:29:56.000Z","msg":"希望大家專心區選先<br />\n你而家出黎只會被捕 黑警拉你坐78 24號就投唔到票<br />\n到時區議會失守 政府就可以大大聲同外媒講市民企佢嗰邊<br />\n係同路人就一定會停一停抖一抖<br />\n邊個阻止區選進行就係鬼 因為客觀效果就係保皇得益<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">11月24日 血債票償 踢走保皇黨</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/vp/250a150e3b7bce618995be275d28ff4e/5E448B03/t51.2885-15/sh0.08/e35/c180.0.1079.1079a/s640x640/70179621_135577684418097_5168140313520011975_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_cat=109\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%2Fvp%2F250a150e3b7bce618995be275d28ff4e%2F5E448B03%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fsh0.08%2Fe35%2Fc180.0.1079.1079a%2Fs640x640%2F70179621_135577684418097_5168140313520011975_n.jpg%3F_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com%26_nc_cat%3D109&h=5380aa8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e924192cec08a4208470f0fd252ea6efc43c1ba","tid":1740000,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:35:38.000Z","msg"